#                         ([PKG-NAME-015] four gates).
#   "-"                 — ruled no-alias (consumers use the qualified form).
# Lines marked [LIVE] are existing shipped aliases (ratify-as-is candidates);
# [?] marks proposals the drafter flags as genuinely arguable.
